Run Script1:
- input: one csv file with point coordinates and other parameters
- output: three kml files (one with the samples 2km bounding boxe and the others are tiling of the AOI for Landsat and Sentinel download)

Load the 3 kml as 3 fusion tables in your personnal space

Run GEE script: https://code.earthengine.google.com/ddb6c4d282d33b1457ed05ea1543d294
- input:  3 fusion table IDs + parameters specific to the acquisition time
- output: time series downloaded to your GoogleDrive

Download from GoogleDrive to a local harddrive

Run Script2:
- input: the path of the harddrive where your Landsat and Sentinel data is stored
- output: a floder containing the time series for each sample
